Package: enviRonmentalContouRs
Title: Fits various environmental contours for marine offshore structure engineering.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul-Adrien", "Alves", , "pauladrien.alves@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides functions for estimating IFORM, Direct Sampling,  HDR, ISORM and D-IFORM contours, as well as joint distribution modeling functions necessary for some contours.
